data.description: Love the country, peacefulness, and nature? Then you will love this log cabin-style home sitting on 2.657 acres behind an electric gate. Knotty pine walls and cabinets make it feel rustic and cozy. Master and secondary are down. Renovated baths in 2023. Upstairs is a loft and a large bedroom with built-in bunk beds. Numerous outbuildings: 800 sqft garage currently used as a CrossFit gym; chicken coop; storage shed with 2 slot carport; boat/RV/storage w hookups; and small barn. Property is fenced and cross-fenced for your animalsâ€”a cool 1/1 apartment in the back of the garage. Enjoy sitting out on your rustic covered patio, entertaining, and enjoying the breeze. 15 min to downtown.
